  "templateWelcome": "# In this file you can add Templates, which serve as easy copy-paste alternatives.\n# To create a template, write a new line with the same formatting as the test Template below.\n# Note that Templates can't be longer than 120 characters and can't contain special characters. Having so will kick you.\n\ntest: this is an example template. Type '/t test' to see it.\n\nwelcome: Welcome! This lobby uses Among Us Revamped {ModVersion} by MV. Enjoy!",
  "moderatorWelcome": "# In this file you can add Moderators by Friendcode.\n# If you add someone, they will gain a purple name in-game.\n# Go to 'System Settings' in-game to customize Moderator permissions. Below is a Friendcode example.\n\nfriendcode#0000",
  "vipWelcome": "# In this file you can add VIP's by Friendcode.\n# If you add someone, they will gain a yellow name in-game.\n# Go to 'System Settings' in-game to customize VIP permissions. Below is a Friendcode example.\n\nfriendcode#0000\n",
  "adminWelcome": "# In this file you can add Admins by Friendcode.\n# If you add someone, they will gain a red name in-game.\n# Go to 'System Settings' in-game to customize Admin permissions. Below is a Friendcode example.\n\nfriendcode#0000\n",
  "banlistWelcome": "# In this file you can ban players from your lobby by Friendcode.\n# Banning someone in-game will automatically add them here as well. Below is a Friendcode example.\n\nfriendcode#0000\n",
